          <span class="eyebrow">Boardwalk field guide</span>
          <h1>Community currents</h1>
          <p class="lede">Where the various Claw crews actually gather, what kind of talk happens there, and which public docks are worth visiting first. This is the social map, not the install map.</p>
        </div>
        <aside class="note-card">
          <img src="/assets/postcards/community-currents.png" alt="Faded postcard-style scene for Community Currents" style="max-width:100%; border-radius:12px; margin-bottom:0.5rem;" />
          <h3>Short read</h3>
          <p>OpenClaw has the strongest centralized public community. NanoClaw and PicoClaw lean more heavily on GitHub Discussions and repo-centric chatter. NemoClaw is still young enough that the official NVIDIA channels matter more than grassroots folklore.</p>
        </aside>
      </div>

